testsuite.name: StudentRepository Sorting Tests

testcase.name: sortByName should sort by last name, then first name, then email
sortByEmailLength should sort by email length
Sorting empty repository should return empty list
sortByName with students having same last and first name should sort by email
sortByNameDesc should sort by last name descending, then first name, then email
Sorting single student should return list with that student
sortByName should not modify the original repository
sortByFirstName should sort by first name
sortByEnrollmentDate should sort by enrollment date ascending
